  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unravel the mystery of a magical labyrinth with Neffy to save the sealed Moon Goddess!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>■■■■ Game Overview ■■■■<br>“<strong>Neffy - Moonlight Labyrinth -</strong>” is a VR action puzzle game where you join Neffy, a novice shrine maiden, on an adventure through a mysterious labyrinth. Solve puzzles and confront magical enemies as you uncover the secrets hidden within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■■■■ You Are the Legendary Hero, Novalis ■■■■<br>Summoned into this world by Neffy, you play as Novalis. However, because Neffy is only a novice, the summoning was incomplete. You'll need to support her by harnessing “Moon Power” gained through the Moon Gems she collects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■■■■ Novalis’s Abilities ■■■■<br><strong>Right Hand: Moon Gauntlet</strong><br>Use Moon Power to activate huge mechanisms or unlock sealed devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Left Hand: Pendant</strong><br>Check your Moon Gem total, Moon Level, and Neffy's status.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>■■■■ Build a Bond with Neffy ■■■■<br>You’ll need to physically interact with Neffy in VR to unlock her full potential. If she’s far away, you can call her back to continue your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ Transform into a Black Cat<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>▼ Recover Health<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>▼ Communicate<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Even players new to VR can enjoy the game thanks to the calm pacing and minimal intense motion.<br><br>Join Neffy on an emotional, warm, and magical journey through the Moonlight Labyrinth—and save her world!<br><br><strong>Neffy’s English voice is performed by Diana Garnet</strong>, bringing her gentle, endearing personality to life and making your adventure all the more immersive.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unravel the mystery of a magical labyrinth with Neffy to save the sealed Moon Goddess!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>■■■■ Game Overview ■■■■<br>“<strong>Neffy - Moonlight Labyrinth -</strong>” is a VR action puzzle game where you join Neffy, a novice shrine maiden, on an adventure through a mysterious labyrinth. Solve puzzles and confront magical enemies as you uncover the secrets hidden within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■■■■ You Are the Legendary Hero, Novalis ■■■■<br>Summoned into this world by Neffy, you play as Novalis. However, because Neffy is only a novice, the summoning was incomplete. You'll need to support her by harnessing “Moon Power” gained through the Moon Gems she collects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■■■■ Novalis’s Abilities ■■■■<br><strong>Right Hand: Moon Gauntlet</strong><br>Use Moon Power to activate huge mechanisms or unlock sealed devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Left Hand: Pendant</strong><br>Check your Moon Gem total, Moon Level, and Neffy's status.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>■■■■ Build a Bond with Neffy ■■■■<br>You’ll need to physically interact with Neffy in VR to unlock her full potential. If she’s far away, you can call her back to continue your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ Transform into a Black Cat<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>▼ Recover Health<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>▼ Communicate<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Even players new to VR can enjoy the game thanks to the calm pacing and minimal intense motion.<br><br>Join Neffy on an emotional, warm, and magical journey through the Moonlight Labyrinth—and save her world!<br><br><strong>Neffy’s English voice is performed by Diana Garnet</strong>, bringing her gentle, endearing personality to life and making your adventure all the more immersive.</p>",
